  "title": "Human Resource Executive",
  "description": "<p>Key Responsibilities</p><p>1.‚Ā† ‚Ā†Onboarding & Employee Administration</p><p>‚ÄĘ‚Ā†  ‚Ā†Coordinate employee onboarding activities, including preparation of Letters of Appointment (LOA) and onboarding documentation.</p><p>‚ÄĘ‚Ā†  ‚Ā†Maintain accurate employee</p><p>‚ÄĘ‚Ā†  ‚Ā†Prepare HR related letters and documentation.</p><p>2.‚Ā† ‚Ā†Work Pass Administration</p><p>‚ÄĘ‚Ā†  ‚Ā†Handle work pass applications, renewals, and cancellations</p><p>‚ÄĘ‚Ā†  ‚Ā†Liaise with MOM, agents, and internal stakeholders on work pass matters.</p><p>3.‚Ā† ‚Ā†Training & Compliance</p><p>‚ÄĘ‚Ā†  ‚Ā†Coordinate training administration, including:</p><p>o\tSourcing training courses and providers</p><p>o\tTracking attendance and completion</p><p>‚ÄĘ‚Ā†  ‚Ā†Maintain up-to-date records of mandatory training requirements and ensure compliance with statutory and internal policies.</p><p>‚ÄĘ‚Ā†  ‚Ā†Support training cost and training hours tracking.</p><p>4.‚Ā† ‚Ā†Employee Life Cycle Management</p><p>‚ÄĘ‚Ā†  ‚Ā†Provide administrative support throughout the employee life cycle, including:</p><p>o\tOnboarding</p><p>o\tConfirmation</p><p>o\tInternal transfers</p><p>o\tSalary adjustments</p><p>o\tCessation</p><p>‚ÄĘ‚Ā†  ‚Ā†Ensure HR processes are consistently applied and properly documented.</p><p>5.‚Ā† ‚Ā†HR Reporting & Support</p><p>‚ÄĘ‚Ā†  ‚Ā†Assist in maintaining HR reports</p><p>‚ÄĘ‚Ā†  ‚Ā†Provide general HR administrative support and respond to basic employee HR queries.</p>",
